  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your existence in a twilight state between life and death makes you difficult to defeat. When damage reduces you to 0 Hit Points, you can make a Charisma saving throw (DC 5 plus the damage taken). On a success, you instead drop to 1 Hit Point. You can't use this feature if you are reduced to 0 Hit Points by Radiant damage or by a Critical Hit.</p><p>After the saving throw succeeds, you cannot use this feature again until you finish a Long Rest, or until you spend a cumulative total of 10 Sorcery Points.</p>",
